{"tid":606643,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國盃 實力弱非大敗藉口 納比：輸在心態","createTime":"2018-03-26T15:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T09:28:25.000Z","uid":2883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3069c0f5784805483edc3fa1ddb5d0f8f397a64a","tid":606643,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"中國於亞洲多屬於實力較強的一方，但在中國盃卻明顯與歐洲球隊有差距，中國主帥賽後有感而發，認為球隊雖然實力較弱，但並不是大敗的藉口：「球員就是要在場上去競爭，拼盡去做好防守，可能每名球員都有不同的想法，但我曾在世界各地比賽，在頂級球隊及聯賽中打滾，在一些外圍賽中我們或會面對實力較低的球隊，但有時間我們仍會落敗，為甚麼？因為對方肯去競爭，不會因為對方是中國隊而退縮，就好像香港兩度守和中國一樣，他們知道自己不是最強，但仍盡力做到最好，不會給予機會對方去做想做的事。他們會做好防守，緊逼每名球員，這就是重點，這種打法不會在15分鐘失3球。」 <br />\n<br />\n納比續指問題出現在球員的心態上，他認為球員無需因身於弱勢而感到害怕，更應團結地築起血肉長城：「就算放20名球員在後防亦沒有用，這不是球員質素的問題，而是只要每名球員都知道他們的位置及應做的事，戰鬥至最後一刻，可能你仍然會輸，但不會輸得如今天般，可能只是輸一、兩球，甚至取得和局。對方可能比你快，比你有技術，但最後他們與我都是一樣，他們不是火星人。我們意大利贏過四次世界盃冠軍，一次歐洲國家盃冠軍，面對巴西及德國等強隊仍可以贏出，這就是心態。」<br />\n<br />\n心態足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8166b9c758fd614430f559572abda9ac4381c23c","tid":606643,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T15:50:32.000Z","msg":"令意大利同 蚛蟈比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n納比都係為錢姐"},{"pid":"ef5d278b4b30febc8f13ed8509131c0d968e2530","tid":606643,"uid":20634,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"祖國加油💪🏻🇨🇳🇭🇰"},{"pid":"e24caa47d949969d5a592f75d6d300d03e045488","tid":606643,"uid":17522,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因為對方肯去競爭，不會因為對方是中國隊而退縮，就好像香港兩度守和中國一樣，他們知道自己不是最強，但仍盡力做到最好，不會給予機會對方去做想做的事。</span><br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afebd17580e4d921065897a08c7b6d4db9ffd497","tid":606643,"uid":33712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"科蘭又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada10228603ee39c3731871684d0fd71fc0a0947","tid":606643,"uid":44457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"廢老科爛潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae32c600254babb196fabac628738673f91da7f","tid":606643,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d434a57f959c496af91d2232056b3aed844d487","tid":606643,"uid":46151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"中國於亞洲多屬於實力較強的一方<br />\n第一句已經fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f1ef3caa9125dcb2319af6febc4dcb3fb703e1","tid":606643,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d434a57f959c496af91d2232056b3aed844d487","tid":606643,"uid":46151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"中國於亞洲多屬於實力較強的一方<br />\n第一句已經fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:51:30.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9d00c43b101d835f914da1c3f2194ba3edb733","tid":606643,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f1ef3caa9125dcb2319af6febc4dcb3fb703e1","tid":606643,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d434a57f959c496af91d2232056b3aed844d487","tid":606643,"uid":46151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"中國於亞洲多屬於實力較強的一方<br />\n第一句已經fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:51:30.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:28:25.000